    "[Execution] Execute the following commands:$./run.sh 5 240 kamailio,pure-ftpd,live555 chatafl,aflnet $./analyze.sh kamailio,pure-ftpd,live555 240[Results] Upon completion of the commands, a folder prefixed with res_ will be generated.",
